name: THE SPIDER
description:
Some years ago in my loneliness I was visited by the raven, I didn't trust him, people say they are terrible creatures, but he came back every day. You can see how this story ended. Today, some time after living with the marks of his attack, I was visited by another creature during the night, a spider, in the darkness of my room I heard it coming down, walking towards me and enveloping me in an endless nightmare. Now I am not afraid, I believe it was always here inside me, protecting itself in the darkness of my soul
